                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Buck</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-03-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 17, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Buck reports that a proposal to arbitrate has been made by the Japanese
                    Government to the representatives of the powers protesting; that the United
                    States, not having protested, is not included, and inquires whether it would be
                    proper to ask that the United States Government be made a party to the
                    arbitration.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
